<p>英 /'juːsləs/    美 /'juːsləs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>无用的；无效的；无价值的:</strong></h4>
<p>反 useful </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The railway tracks were now useless pieces of steel.
铁轨如今变成了一条条废钢材。</p><footer>人教① – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s useless worrying about it. 
为这件事担心无济于事。</p></div></div>